videoDetails.title: Hazrat Nuh AS Ki Qaum Ne Allah Ki Warnings Ko Ignore Kiya |     | Quran Stories
videoDetails.shortDescription:
Allah ne Hazrat Nuh   ki qaum ko kyun gharq kar diya?

Is video mein hum Quran ki roshni mein   ki pur asrar kahani dekhte hain  un ka shirk, un ka inkaar, Hazrat Nuh AS ka sabr, aur aakhir ka wo azaab jo qayamat tak ke liye  ban gaya.

Ye powerful Quran waqiya aapko batayegi:

 Hazrat Nuh AS ko nabuwat kyun di gayi?

 Qaum e Nuh ne un ki dawat ko kaise reject kiya?

 Kashti e Nuh ka waqia  kaun bach gaya, kaun doob gaya?

 Aaj ke zamane ke liye is kahani mein kaun sa hidden message hai?

0:00  Introdution  Qaum e Nuh AS
1:25 Qaum e Nuh AS Ki Qaum Ka Gunnah
3:00  Hazrat Nuh AS Ka Mission  950 Saal Ki Dawat
3:40  Qaum e Nuh Ka Allah Ki Baat Na Maanna
4:20  Hazrat Nuh AS Ne Kia Badua Di?
4:45  Allah Ki Taraf Se Aakhri Warning
6:05  Azaab Ka Aghaz
9:45  Kashti e Nuh Me Kaun Bacha?
10:15  Hamare Liye Sabak Or Aaj Ke Zamanay Ke Liye Paighaam


 Quranic References (Hazrat Nuh AS & Qaum e Nuh):

 Surah Hud (11:2549)

 Surah Al-Muminun (23:2330)

 Surah Al-Qamar (54:917)

 Surah Nuh (71:128)

Agar aapko Islamic stories, Prophet stories, aur Quranic waqiat pasand hain, ye video aap ke liye hai.

Aap se sirf 3 kaam:

1 Video ko end tak dekhein  har second ek sabak hai

2 Isko family & friends ke saath share karein  shayad kisi ki zindagi badal jaye

3 Channel ko subscribe karein aur bell icon dabayen taake aap Imaan Verse ki next Quran stories miss na karein

 Comments mein zaroor likhein:

Aapko Hazrat Nuh AS ke Waqiya ka kaun sa hissa sab se zyada hila dene wala laga?

My Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hassandar26

#ImaanVerse #HazratNuhAS #QaumENuh #IslamicStories #QuranStories #Noah
